<div id="mm-recipes-intro_1-0" class="comp mm-recipes-intro mntl-block"><div id="mm-recipes-intro__jump-to-recipe_1-0" class="comp mm-recipes-intro__jump-to-recipe foodandwine-jump-to-recipe mm-recipes-jump-to-recipe mntl-block"><button id="mm-recipes-jump-to-recipe__button_1-0" class="comp mm-recipes-jump-to-recipe__button mntl-button text-label-300 button--contained-standard"> Jump to recipe
<svg class="icon icon-arrow-down mntl-button__icon "
>
<use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#icon-arrow-down" href="#icon-arrow-down"></use>
</svg>
</button></div>
<div id="mm-recipes-intro__content_1-0" class="comp mm-recipes-intro__content mntl-sc-page mntl-block" data-sc-sticky-offset="190" data-sc-ad-label-height="24" data-sc-ad-track-spacing="100" data-sc-min-track-height="250" data-sc-max-track-height="600" data-sc-breakpoint="50em" data-sc-load-immediate="1" data-sc-content-positions="[1, 1250, 1550, 1950, 2350, 2750, 3150, 3550, 3950]" data-bind-scroll-on-start="true"><p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html"> Nowadays, you can find a version of warm, gooey lava cake on many restaurant menus, but the original is in a class of its own. Molten chocolate cake is highly sought-after for many reasons; at the top of the list is the dessert's unique texture and filling, as a cakey exterior houses a decadent center of flowing, warm dark chocolate. The first time you try one, it may seem like magic, but this chocolate lava cake recipe is actually quite easy to make and ready to serve in under an hour.&nbsp;The key is to use the finest-quality <a href="https://www.foodandwine.com/best-chocolate-for-baking-7099448" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="internalLink" data-ordinal="1">chocolate</a> — it will make a big difference in the end.
</p>
<div id="mntl-sc-block_2-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div>
<div id="mntl-sc-block_3-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block foodandwine-sc-block-featuredlink mm-myrecipes-sc-featured-link mntl-sc-block-universal-featured-link mntl-sc-block-universal-featured-link--related"><a
href="https://www.foodandwine.com/desserts/cake/chocolate-cake/molten-chocolate-cake"
rel="nocaes"
id="mntl-sc-block-universal-featured-link__link_1-0"
class="mntl-sc-block-universal-featured-link__link mntl-text-link text-utility-300 global-link"
data-tracking-container="true"
data-tracking-id="featured-link"
><span class="link__wrapper">Make Molten Chocolate Cake at Home and Be Happy</span></a>
</div>
<div id="mntl-sc-block_4-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div>
<div id="mntl-sc-block_5-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block foodandwine-sc-block-faq mntl-sc-block-universal-faq theme-expanded"><span class="heading-toc" id="toc-faq-87287e50-903e-4fb4-b655-fa027c7d5c26"></span>
<h2 class="mntl-sc-block-universal-faq__title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
<ul id="mntl-sc-block-universal-faq__content_1-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block-universal-faq__content mntl-accordion ">
<li class="accordion__item js-accordion-item is-active" data-ordinal="1">
<div tabindex="-1" class="accordion__header js-accordion-trigger" id="mntl-accordion__item_1-0-section-0">
<span class="accordion__title">How can you tell if molten lava cake is done?</span>
</div><!--end accordion__header-->
<div class="accordion__body">
<div id="mntl-accordion__content_1-0" class="comp mntl-accordion__content"> <div class="faq-accordion__item-answer">
<p>The best way to tell if molten chocolate lava cake is done is by analyzing its surface. Once the tops of the cakes are just set and have a light spring when poked, the cake should be fully cooked. (The center should still have a slight jiggle.) However, a toothpick can help determine the cake&#39;s doneness with greater certainty; it should come out clean when inserted in the outer edges of the cake but should leave some residue from the batter when inserted in the center.</p>
</div>
</div> </div><!--end accordion__body-->
</li><!--end accordion__item-->
<li class="accordion__item js-accordion-item is-active" data-ordinal="2">
<div tabindex="-1" class="accordion__header js-accordion-trigger" id="mntl-accordion__item_2-0-section-1">
<span class="accordion__title">How long do you heat up lava cake?</span>
</div><!--end accordion__header-->
<div class="accordion__body">
<div id="mntl-accordion__content_2-0" class="comp mntl-accordion__content"> <div class="faq-accordion__item-answer">
<p>Lava cake can be reheated after being refrigerated or frozen. If it hasn&#39;t been thawed, reheat it in a 400ºF oven for roughly 15 minutes. If it&#39;s coming from the refrigerator, nine minutes in a 350ºF oven should do the trick.</p>
</div>
</div> </div><!--end accordion__body-->
</li><!--end accordion__item-->
</ul><!--end accordion --></div>
<div id="mntl-sc-block_6-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div>
<span class="heading-toc" id="toc-notes-from-the-food--wine-test-kitchen"></span><h2 id="mntl-sc-block_7-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block foodandwine-sc-block-heading mntl-sc-block-heading"> <span class="mntl-sc-block-heading__text"> Notes from the Food &amp; Wine Test Kitchen </span> </h2>
<p id="mntl-sc-block_8-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html"> These gooey, decadent cakes are enough on their own, but you can serve them with sweetened whipped cream or vanilla ice cream if you like. Molten chocolate cake is easily one of the ultimate desserts for intimate special occasions, such as <a href="https://www.foodandwine.com/holidays-events/valentines-day/valentines-day-dinner" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="internalLink" data-ordinal="1">Valentine's Day</a>: It's simple, sexy, and indulgent. For an extra surprise, try one of these recipes for <a href="https://www.foodandwine.com/recipes/molten-chocolate-cake-caramel-filling" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="internalLink" data-ordinal="2">molten cakes filled with caramel</a> or <a href="https://www.foodandwine.com/recipes/molten-chocolate-cake-raspberry-filling" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="internalLink" data-ordinal="3">molten cakes filled with raspberry sauce</a>.
</p>
<div id="mntl-sc-block_9-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div>
<span class="heading-toc" id="toc-make-ahead"></span><h2 id="mntl-sc-block_10-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block foodandwine-sc-block-heading mntl-sc-block-heading"> <span class="mntl-sc-block-heading__text"> Make ahead </span> </h2>
<p id="mntl-sc-block_11-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html"> The batter can be refrigerated for several hours; simply bring it to room temperature before baking. The fully cooked molten chocolate cakes can also be refrigerated for up to three days or frozen for up to one month in an airtight container.
</p>
<div id="mntl-sc-block_12-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div>
<span class="heading-toc" id="toc-suggested-pairing"></span><h2 id="mntl-sc-block_13-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block foodandwine-sc-block-heading mntl-sc-block-heading"> <span class="mntl-sc-block-heading__text"> Suggested pairing </span> </h2>
<p id="mntl-sc-block_14-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html"> Chocolate is too intense and bitter for many sweet wines, but not port. Try this dessert with a ruby port that&#39;ll complement the rich chocolate in the lava cake.
</p></div></div>
