<p id="mntl-sc-block_33-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html"> Beat eggs, egg yolks, sugar, and salt in a medium bowl with an electric mixer fitted with the whisk attachment on high speed until thickened and pale, 2 to 3 minutes
</p>
