<p id="mntl-sc-block_38-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html"> Whisk melted chocolate until smooth.
</p>
<div id="mntl-sc-block_39-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div>
</LI>
