</figcaption></figure>
<p id="mntl-sc-block_43-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html"> Quickly fold melted chocolate mixture and flour into egg mixture in bowl until well combined and no streaks remain.
</p>
<div id="mntl-sc-block_44-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div>
</LI>
