</figcaption></figure>
<p id="mntl-sc-block_48-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html"> Spoon batter into prepared ramekins (about 1/2 cup per ramekin) and smooth the top using a small offset spatula if needed. Place baking sheet with ramekins in the preheated oven; bake until tops of cakes are just set and edges spring back when touched but centers still feel soft, about 9 to 12 minutes.
</p>
<div id="mntl-sc-block_49-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div>
</LI>
<LI id="mntl-sc-block_51-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup mntl-sc-block-group--LI">
